members.name: Jane Doe
members.bio: A team member, Roshan reached out to me about being a mentor. As I already had previous experience and enjoyed robotics I decided to get involved. Past experiences in FRC: Although I don't have much experience in FRC, I have a lot of experience in VEX robotics. I was the co-captain of my high school team, which had performed to the state level. Past experiences: I am currently a student at North Carolina State University pursuing a double degree in computer and electrical engineering. In addition to this, I was the co-captain of the robotic team in high school and was in the offroad racing team at NC State.
